description.en: MIM, built on the Solana blockchain, is a community of music producers, recording artists, visual artists, video makers and designers collectively producing content engaging with the metaverse. Primarily realised in the form of virtual artists, sample packs/producer tools, releases, clothing and NFTS, the community forms a larger swarm where tasks are undertaken in clusters to evolve beyond the traditional means of cultural production.
